
Ranger Help for: treat
======================

SYNTAX:      treat/treat <target>
USAGE:       forest,plains,jungle,swamp,desert
SLOT COST:   10
BASE SP:     variable
SKILL TYPE:  defensive

SUMMARY:    
With this skill, in certain terrains, a Ranger can use native ingredients
to make heals and treat the wounds of a friend or him or herself. Too treat
oneself, just type 'treat' with no argument. As a Ranger's knowledge of
the environment increases, so does the effectiveness of his or her heals.

